subject: Nominate Leaders for the Future of America
body: Be a Part of History – Nominate Leaders for a Healthier Republic NOMINATE OURFUTURE LEADERSYour Nominations Can Help Drain the SwampDear Peter,PresidentTrump, Robert F. Kennedy Jr., and the unity coalition need your help innominating individuals of integrity and courage for over 4,000 appointments inthe future Trump Administration. This isn’t the old system of backroom deals;this is your chance to shape the administration through the newNomineesForThePeople.com .Restore America’s Health and IntegrityThe MakeAmerica Healthy Again movement isn’t just about keeping our bodies healthy andtoxin-free—it’s about restoring the Republic by draining the swamp and endingcorporate influence. We can’t rely on the same revolving-door D.C. crowd. Weneed the best public servants our country has to offer—and we believe you knowwho they are.Nominate Someone TodaySubmit your nominations for those youbelieve should serve. These can be public figures, those you know, or evenyourself.👉 Submit Your Nomination Here Nominees are needed across all areas ofgovernment such as: - • Health, Food, and Agriculture - • Housing, Economy,and Environment & Natural Resources - • Education, Labor, Peace at Home, andPeace Abroad - • Technology and Government Efficiency Your input is essential.Please participate as soon as you can before November 5th to help rally andmotivate our community in these final days before Election Day. Yournominations will play a role in supporting Bobby’s work on the Transition Teamand within the future unity administration.Share This OpportunityEncouragefriends and family to join in—share NomineesForThePeople.com widely so otherscan nominate and comment on future leaders too.We’re excited to read yoursubmissions and to see the vibrant discussions around these nominees. Yourfeedback on the site is also welcomed!Thanks for being a part of this historicmovement to bring the people’s voice to Washington.Nominate Now atNomineesForThePeople.com Team KennedyMahanow.org ©2024 • Unsubscribe •Privacy Policy • Terms of Use • Contact Us PAID FOR BY TEAM KENNEDY -=-=-Team Kennedy - CA 90049, United States This email was sent todpwillis67@gmail.com.
